{
  "1839930": {
    "name": "Lifecraft",
    "steam_appid": 1839930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Lifecraft是一款生存游戏，你从一个简单的细胞开始，努力通过吸收原始汤中的资源来生存。<br><br>通过进化，你将能够慢慢地成为一个更先进的生物，必须处理所有的好处和缺点：你将需要更多的能量，更复杂的资源，你将必须管理更高级别的过程（例如消化，循环）来生存：你将成为一个由许多子系统组成的完全成熟的生物，这些子系统必须在完美的平衡中合作。<br><br>每个子系统都将有自己的特点和管理方式，最终迫使你在所有子系统之间创建协同效应。<br><br>除此之外，还会有来自可能的疾病的外部或内部干扰：病毒，细菌，需要治愈的伤口等等。<br><br>一旦为这个微观世界设定了规则，游戏的可能性就无穷无尽了！<br><br><br><br><strong>特性</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/66badb15df1cc81258f2c042deb29484.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/66badb15df1cc81258f2c042deb29484.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/66badb15df1cc81258f2c042deb29484.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>燃烧：能量是游戏的关键方面，你将能够通过糖酵解甚至线粒体呼吸来产生ATP，这可以被认为是储存在电池中的能量！能量将被用来为细胞内外的建筑供电。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/340ffee9d1df07061d1020a2e750f34b.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/340ffee9d1df07061d1020a2e750f34b.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/340ffee9d1df07061d1020a2e750f34b.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>进化：进化将让玩家发现新的游戏元素，这将使生物更复杂，但能够变得越来越大！从循环开始，到大脑和神经元。将会有一些实用的进化步骤，用来给你更好的工具来优化所有的物流。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/1e4ca55df39d8aa77c17d51027026add.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/1e4ca55df39d8aa77c17d51027026add.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/1e4ca55df39d8aa77c17d51027026add.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>成长：你开始时是一个小生物，很快你就需要扩大以腾出更多的空间，获取外部汤中更好和新颖的资源。这将通过生产所需的脚手架和组织材料，在你想要的任何地方逐块扩展来完成！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/2daf6e14585b4bcbc200500d3e48c6c7.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/2daf6e14585b4bcbc200500d3e48c6c7.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/2daf6e14585b4bcbc200500d3e48c6c7.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>供应：一旦生物足够大，用微管在建筑物之间运输物品将不够。此外，没有办法直接运输细胞外的材料，所以循环将是基础。你将需要泵，动脉，静脉和毛细血管来供应或带走材料。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/6761725f115793f61a5db7935d10b4c1.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/6761725f115793f61a5db7935d10b4c1.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/6761725f115793f61a5db7935d10b4c1.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>防御：病毒，细菌，真菌和寄生虫。外面有很多危险的东西！你需要使用你的免疫系统来击败这些威胁！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/47a636d10987dd445ab079657c4080d8.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/47a636d10987dd445ab079657c4080d8.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/47a636d10987dd445ab079657c4080d8.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>生存：一个运作正常的生物需要一些参数在正确的范围内保持稳定，这就是所谓的稳态。温度，氧气，pH值都是需要调节的参数，以避免死亡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/ae02153c2eba7bc8c0c9de9c5bf3bd73.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/ae02153c2eba7bc8c0c9de9c5bf3bd73.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/ae02153c2eba7bc8c0c9de9c5bf3bd73.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>治愈：如果生物受伤了怎么办？它需要治愈，可能通过止血来阻止出血，然后通过组织再生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/37544497fd3dafb7875541cbcd552b21.poster.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/37544497fd3dafb7875541cbcd552b21.webm?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/37544497fd3dafb7875541cbcd552b21.mp4?t=1736887145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>呼吸：一个生物使用的大部分能量是由细胞呼吸产生的，这需要氧气并产生二氧化碳。为了吸入前者和呼出后者，你将需要与你的循环系统连接的呼吸组织。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/cf0c0b23f780125cb392341cea9b6ebf.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>消化：在游戏开始时，需要简单的资源，但在游戏后期，你将需要将复杂的资源（食物）消化成基本元素，你将需要牙齿，胃和肠。你还需要合成大量的酶，这些酶在整个过程中都会用到。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/511ba345670f64cab3709972a417f086.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>排泄：好吧，所有没有被用作资源的东西对生物来说都是无用的，可能对生物有毒。这就是为什么你需要一种方法来通过肾脏过滤掉毒素，但也需要通过其他方式排除无用的材料。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/d27b7ad7cf6f8de09ea27d5b61623806.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>思考：在某些时候，生物可能希望通过更精细的调节来自动管理子系统，这就是神经元的作用：通过传感器和逻辑，你将能够设定特定的规则，这将使生物的行为自动化。<br><br><strong>路线图</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839930/extras/91b15c498b2204c67a73a92f71250d30.avif?t=1736887145\" width=600 height=1099 /></span>",
